#MOBILES
#2000
townguard knight~
A Silver Knight~
A powerful knight in silver armor makes his rounds across the room.
~
A knight from the grand castle, Camelot, this human will do whatever
it takes to protect the city of Jad from intruders. Wearing full
silver battle armor, and wielding a huge silver sword, this knight
means business.
~
