innkeeper~
Mike, The Innkeeper~
A young man is here snapping his fingers as he sways to a silent beat.
~
The owner of the Cruising Sailors Inn, Mike is well known for his
good services, clean beds and hot ready meals for those wishing to stay
at his inn, regardless of the time they come in. The only annoying thing
about him is that he is ALWAYS doing some silly dance.
~
